message: Hi Bob, let's start with a fair split. I'll take $60, you get $40. This gives us both a good starting point. What do you say?

Alright Alice, since you weren't happy with a 60/40 split, I'm going to take a bit more for myself this round. I'll take $60 and you get $40.  Remember, the longer we take, the less my share is worth!
